---
import DefaultBody from '../layouts/DefaultBody.astro';
import Hero   from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BackToTop from '../components/BackToTop.astro';
---

<DefaultBody title="Department of Beta Testing - ATPLLC" description="AT Products LLC's DoBT beta tests versions during development before shipping!" keywords="AT Products, Ethical Hacking Society, The Script Community, AT Products LLC, ATproducts" author="Alex Toucan" 
  bulletin={[
    { bulletinImage: "TESTINGSLIDE-1.webp" },
    { bulletinImage: "TESTINGSLIDE-2.webp" },
    { bulletinImage: "TESTINGSLIDE-3.webp" },
  ]} 
>
  <div id="page">
    <Navbar />
    <div id="main-content">
      <Hero
        id="codinghome"
        titleHTML="<h1 class='display-3 fw-bold'>AT Products LLC</h1> <h3 class='display-6 text-body-secondary fw-medium'>Department of Beta Testing</h3>"
        description="Welcome to AT Products's Department of Beta Testing's website portal!"
        primaryHref="https://beta.atproducts.xyz/"
        primaryText="Beta Website"
        secondaryHref="https://atproducts.xyz/"
        secondaryText="Main Website"
        marginBottom="false"
        icons={[
          { icon: "github", desc: "GitHub", href: "https://github.com/Alex-Toucan/atproducts.xyz" },
          { icon: "twitter-x", desc: "Twitter / X", href: "https://twitter.com/ATProductsLLC" },
          { icon: "youtube", desc: "YouTube", href: "https://youtube.com/c/AlexToucanAT" },
          { icon: "envelope-fill", desc: "Contact Form / Email", href: "https://atproducts.xyz/form/" },
          { icon: "cloud-sun-fill", desc: "Weather", href: "https://twitter.com/ATPWeather" },
        ]}
      />
      <div id="carousel-A" class="carousel carousel-main carousel-fade slide shadow px-0 container-xsm mt-xmd-2 mb-3 pointer-event" data-bs-ride="carousel"> 
        <div class="pt-xmd-2 px-xmd-2">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="10000">
              <img src="/media/slideshow/TESTINGSLIDE-1.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt="Testing Slide 1">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="10000">
              <img src="/media/slideshow/TESTINGSLIDE-2.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt="Testing Slide 2">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="10000">
              <img src="/media/slideshow/TESTINGSLIDE-3.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt="Testing Slide 3">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mediarow py-2" aria-label="Carousel-A Controls">
            <button class="carousel-control-prev col" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-A" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <div class="carousel-indicators col-7 col-sm-6 text-center">
              <button aria-label="Slide 1" class="active slidebtn" data-bs-slide-to="0" data-bs-target="#carousel-A" type="button" aria-current="true"></button>
              <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-A" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2" class="slidebtn"></button>
              <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-A" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3" class="slidebtn"></button>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-next col" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-A" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex">
          <div class="btn-group w-100 p-1" role="group" aria-label="Carousel-A Play/Pause">
            <input type="radio" class="btn-check btn-check-dark col playButton" name="btnradio" id="playButton" aria-label="playButton" checked="">
            <label class="btn" for="playButton" id="playButtonLabel"><i class="bi bi-play-fill fs-4 link-carousel"></i></label>
            <input type="radio" class="btn-check btn-check-dark col pauseButton" name="btnradio" id="pauseButton" aria-label="pauseButton">
            <label class="btn" for="pauseButton" id="pauseButtonLabel"><i class="bi bi-pause-fill fs-4 link-carousel"></i></label>
          </div>
          <div class="col px-2 my-auto"> <a href="/media/pdf/Testing Slides.pdf" aria-label="Carousel PDF Download" class="fs-2 link-carousel" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="bi bi-filetype-pdf"></i></a> </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <main id="index" class="container">
        <hr class="hero-drappear">
        <div id="about-us">
          <h2>About Us</h2>
          <p>Welcome to the Department of Beta Testing (DoBT) at AT Products LLC (ATPLLC). Our abbreviations are recognized as ATPLLC-DoBT (full and regularly used), or ATPDoBT (shorter name used). We are dedicated to testing and improving the <a href="https://atproducts.xyz">main department's website</a> to enhance the user experience for our current and future customers.</p>
          <p>Join us in shaping the future of our platform! As a beta tester, your contributions are invaluable. Your feedback helps us identify and address issues, refine features, and ensure a seamless experience for all users.</p>
          <p>Why not <a href="/apply">apply today</a>? Your insights and suggestions can make a significant difference. We greatly appreciate our beta testers' time and effort in helping us achieve excellence.</p>
          <p>Our goals include:</p>
          <ul>
              <li>Identifying and resolving bugs and glitches to enhance website functionality.</li>
              <li>Gathering user feedback to improve usability and user interface design.</li>
              <li>Testing new features and functionalities to meet user expectations and needs.</li>
              <li>Ensuring compatibility across various devices, browsers, and platforms.</li>
              <li>Providing timely updates and enhancements to keep the website dynamic and engaging.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Since March 18th, 2024, the Department of Beta Testing has been crucial in developing and refining AT Products LLC's online presence and has been improving our metrics.</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="what-new">
          <h2> What's New? </h2>
          <p>
            <b>Released on:</b> May 10th, 2025.<br>
            <b>ATP Database:</b> DoBT v2.5.1
          </p>
          <b>Changed</b>
          <ul>
            <li>Revamped the README file.</li>
            <li>Import packages via npm instead of the script tag.</li>
            <li>Import styles via Astro imports.</li>
            <li>Use the more up to date &lt;DefaultBody&gt; tag.</li>
            <li>Updated Astro from v5.7.0 to v5.7.12.</li>
            <li>Updated @astrojs/react from v4.2.4 to v4.2.7.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </main>
      <Footer />
    </div>
    <BackToTop />
  </div>
</DefaultBody>
